rc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</div>\n\n\t\t\t<a id=\"top\"></a>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"mw-indicators mw-body-content\">\n</div>\n\t\t\t<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\" lang=\"en\">Crystal ball of fixation</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"bodyContent\" class=\"mw-body-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"siteSub\" class=\"noprint\">From CrawlWiki</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"contentSub\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"jump-to-nav\" class=\"mw-jump\">\n\t\t\t\t\tJump to:\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#mw-head\">navigation</a>, \t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#p-search\">search</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div style=\"border: 1px solid #f00; background-color: #fcc; border-left: 15px solid #f00; margin-bottom: 20px; width: 100%; padding: 4px 10px; line-height: 1.1em; width: auto;\"><i><b>Obsolete</b>: This article refers to an aspect of the game which has been removed. It is retained for historical reference only.</i></div>\n<table style=\"background:#f5faff; border:1px solid #cedff2; width:auto; margin: 0px 5%; margin-bottom:1.25em; font-style:italic; text-align:left; color:#000; padding:1.5em 1em;\">\n\n<tr>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 100%;\"> A dangerous item which hypnotizes anyone so unwise as to gaze into it, leaving them helpless for a significant length of time.\n</td></tr></table>\n<p>A <b>crystal ball of fixation</b> is an evocable item which, when used \"successfully\", leaves you <a href=\"/Paralyze\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Paralyze\">paralyzed</a> and <a href=\"/Slow\" title=\"Slow\">slow</a> for 100 turns. This makes you easy prey for any wandering monsters that find you. On a failure, you suffer a <a href=\"/Divinations\" title=\"Divinations\">Divinations</a> <a href=\"/Miscast_effect\" title=\"Miscast effect\">miscast effect</a>, such as losing all <a href=\"/MP\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"MP\">MP</a>, taking <a href=\"/Intelligence\" title=\"Intelligence\">intelligence</a> damage, or being <a href=\"/Confused\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Confused\">confused</a> for 10-20 turns. This item serves no purpose except to make players cautious about testing unidentified crystal balls.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span></h2>\n<p>These were removed in <a href=\"/0.8\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"0.8\">0.8</a>.  Before that, they were a source of numerous amusing deaths.\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240916212838\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0.002 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.020 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.025 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 13/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 48/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 681/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 126/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    8.662      1 -total\n 49.26%    4.267      1 Template:Obsolete\n 49.13%    4.256      1 Template:Flavour\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key crawl_wiki-crawl_:pcache:idhash:4571-0!canonical and timestamp 20240916212838 and revision id 8467\n -->\n</div>\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"printfooter\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRetrieved from \"<a dir=\"ltr\" href=\"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/index.php?title=Crystal_ball_of_fixation&amp;oldid=8467\">http://crawl.chaosforge.org/index.php?title=Crystal_ball_of_fixation&amp;oldid=8467</a>\"\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"catlinks\" class=\"catlinks\" data-mw=\"interface\"><div id=\"mw-normal-catlinks\" class=\"mw-normal-catlinks\"><a href=\"/Special:Categories\" title=\"Special:Categories\">Categories</a>: <ul><li><a href=\"/Category:Obsolete_articles\" title=\"Category:Obsolete articles\">Obsolete articles</a></li><li><a href=\"/Category:Obsolete\"